name: Call Logs Report
query:
SELECT
 date(creation) as "Date::100",
 phone_number as "Contact Number::120",
 contact_person as "Contact Person::120",
 client as "Client::120", 
 time(start_time) as "Start Time::100",
 time(end_time) as "End Time::100",
 TIMEDIFF(time(start_time),time(end_time)) as "Call Length::150",
 call_attendant as "Agent/Call attendant::150",
 name as "call Log Id:Link/Call Logs:150"
FROM
 `tabCall Logs` 
order by
 name asc;
